#### 2) first run  The peak physical memory is 10G+, and the query ends down to 800M.
- Process tracker peak 11G;
- The peak value of query mem tracker is 6.5G, and the tracker value is 2.1G before the end; (In the past, query mem tracker values were negative.)
- The peak value of Orphan tracker is 5.1G, of which the peak value of Bthread tracker is 463M, the peak value of tcmalloc - cache is 350M, and the whereabouts of the remaining 4.3G of Orphan is unknown...

